data.title: The Trusts Arena (Auckland): Events & Tickets
data.meta_description: Find all the available events at The Trusts Arena. Experience the most that Auckland has to offer!
data.text:
The Trusts Arena

Trusts Arena is a modern indoor facility in Auckland that can host various events, including sports, concerts, and corporate meetings. It has a seating capacity of 5,000 and an adjacent track and field with a capacity of 3,000.

All experiences in The Trusts Arena

There aren't any active events in The Trusts Arena.

But you can take a look at all the events we have in Auckland

See events in Auckland
